channel.title: It's been years - and I am curious
channel.description:
Edit: Well, of course I was right. This IS an improper forum to post in. :( If you must, then lock this, but hey at least it's a decent question to ask.
Hey guys, I am VERY sure all of you forgot about me. ;)
Anyways, it has been just about 2+ years since I have last visited the RSCC (RuneScape Cheating Community) and I just wanted to ask how the private server development has been going?
I'm not necessarily interested in developing private servers anymore and bots, well, I got tired of getting banned from RS. :rolleyes:
So ya! What's the progress with private servers nowadays? I've noticed a server advertising in HD graphics and another server with... player wings (interesting!). If you would consider this the wrong forum, then sorry, just making a quick post.
If you do remember me, let me know! ;D
~Dizzy
